des:
We have come up with many ideas of funny things you shouldn't do in a lift so you don't have to. Are you bored, or are you genuinely looking for things you shouldn't do in a lift? Either way, this skill is sure to keep you entertained. 

With new ideas being added all the time, you'll be sure to get plenty of new and unique ideas.
